text: Phryneta flavescens is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1954. It is known from Tanzania.BioLib.cz - Phryneta flavescens. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1954
